{"tid":508722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［帽已綠?] 黑人妻生出「白膚藍眼」女兒　","createTime":"2017-12-24T13:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T08:10:55.000Z","uid":72478,"like":144,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"416d844ba8a4a57938a90452990882d14d590190","tid":508722,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20100721/large/21we1p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100721%2Flarge%2F21we1p.jpg&h=b33eb61e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國60歲的白人退休銷售經理柏金斯（Christopher Perkins）和牙買加籍黑人妻子布雷克（Sophia Blake）結婚後生下一女，原本兩人以為女兒的膚色應該是黑混白的咖啡色，不料女兒生得一身白皙皮膚，還有一雙藍色眼睛，連老婆都不禁問，「這真的是我女兒嗎？」，柏金斯也被陌生人暗示「戴綠帽」。醫生解釋，其實女兒情況相當罕見，是「百萬分之一」的孩子。<br />\n<br />\nsouce: <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171224/1078817.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20171224%2F1078817.htm&d=AwnFYw5fpi2uRqQmtchf6ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=7e7c9918\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171224/1078817.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f2895fcfb5e78865618d5ee1cae765d4b22a8024","tid":508722,"uid":70684,"like":957,"dislike":6,"score":951,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:55:09.000Z","msg":"醫生好有可疑"},{"pid":"d151db6fc68c5d05f6658cae3431bc8a2d61ca90","tid":508722,"uid":45518,"like":296,"dislike":3,"score":293,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:58:29.000Z","msg":"篇文內容同張相唔配合"},{"pid":"c029c38672802ad42ae85d23229f88b210b84c34","tid":508722,"uid":72478,"like":3,"dislike":136,"score":-133,"quote":{"pid":"d151db6fc68c5d05f6658cae3431bc8a2d61ca90","tid":508722,"uid":45518,"like":296,"dislike":3,"score":293,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:58:29.000Z","msg":"篇文內容同張相唔配合"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:10:39.000Z","msg":"唔記得加返示意圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔好意思<br />\n個男人應該係白人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/