且，」老人又說，「告訴你，她最近懷孕了！」<br />\n<br />\n醫生靜靜地聽著，一言不發，「怎麼樣？」老人得意洋洋地說，「不錯罷？」<br />\n<br />\n醫生抬起頭，看了他一眼。「這讓我想起一位失散多年的朋友。他跟我說過一個故事，是他在非洲狩獵時遇上的事。當時他在草原上遇到一頭獅子，他立刻從背上抓下槍來瞄準。然而，他立刻發現他錯了，他拿到的是雨傘，不是槍。這時已經太遲，獅子正站在他面前，就要撲過來，他只好把雨傘扛在肩上，使盡吃奶的力氣『砰砰砰』大叫三聲，奇跡發生了，那獅子竟然倒下死掉啦。」<br />\n<br />\n「狗屎，這怎麼可能」老人大叫，「那一定是別人幹的！」<br />\n<br />\n「我也這麼認為」醫生說.....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4941256301267b40e84a16ab636a4169a6bdc6","tid":508722,"uid":110339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T21:19:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">you are not the father</span></span>"},{"pid":"fb02fac99e09fc44a46bff4896cab8736c022592","tid":508722,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"672d6d91e7f1190cf50e685a0109647abd0acee9","tid":508722,"uid":54490,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:55:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T21:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb7fc6248adc55d482d231d1be09a2edf7325c8","tid":508722,"uid":49004,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T21:43:11.000Z","msg":"陳凱琳老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次睇次次笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691b01c88b1f8ca58dbbccecceda19f41a3bc12e","tid":508722,"uid":61443,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cf761239f3622373e2ae444572ae830b47a33642","tid":508722,"uid":20867,"like":61,"dislike":3,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"一個八十歲的老人去做健康檢查。檢查途中，老人不斷向醫生炫耀他新婚的妻子多好多好。<br />\n<br />\n「他才二十五歲！」老人叫道，「我們結婚四個月，你知道她對我有多忠誠，她無時無刻不需要我，粘我粘到我都感到厭煩了！」「而且，」老人又說，「告訴你，她最近懷孕了！」<br />\n<br />\n醫生靜靜地聽著，一言不發，「怎麼樣？」老人得意洋洋地說，「不錯罷？」<br />\n<br />\n醫生抬起頭，看了他一眼。「這讓我想起一位失散多年的朋友。他跟我說過一個故事，是他在非洲狩獵時遇上的事。當時他在草原上遇到一頭獅子，他立刻從背上抓下槍來瞄準。然而，他立刻發現他錯了，他拿到的是雨傘，不是槍。這時已經太遲，獅子正站在他面前，就要撲過來，他只好把雨傘扛在肩上，使盡吃奶的力氣『砰砰砰』大叫三聲，奇跡發生了，那獅子竟然倒下死掉啦。」<br />\n<br />\n「狗屎，這怎麼可能」老人大叫，「那一定是別人幹的！」<br />\n<br />\n「我也這麼認為」醫生說....."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T22:02:31.000Z","msg":"入黎就係睇 80歲廢老潮文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99337215cb021f7eef31f60042ef6b0c375d609","tid":508722,"uid":102700,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T22:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳凱琳老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次睇次次笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似話佢老婆係印度餐廳做過？"},{"pid":"fcb5a7d2dfe602ac9f6aa57c09e0f22c9abed3eb","tid":508722,"uid":49004,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d99337215cb021f7eef31f60042ef6b0c375d609","tid":508722,"uid":102700,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T22:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳凱琳老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次睇次次笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似話佢老婆係印度餐廳做過？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T22:25:01.000Z","msg":"某間中東餐館老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16123f400b8e297a7bcc22c487e0551b735ef66","tid":508722,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T23:01:39.000Z","msg":"白人就係咁演化出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48169be9abc087bcd9b262ac8ad7e9ddccee7ae6","tid":508722,"uid":26658,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fcb5a7d2dfe602ac9f6aa57c09